org.forgerock.openam.scripting.service

Interface ScriptingService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScriptConfigurationService

    public interface ScriptingService
    An interface for access to the persisted instances of the provided type. It is the layer on top of the ScriptingDataStore, which is responsible for access to all the persisted scripting related data.
    Since:
    13.0.0
